HEADWORD: Formulary
<hw>For"mu*la*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>formulaire</ets>. See <er>Formula</er>.]</ety> <def>Stated;
prescribed; ritual.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

