==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Formulary
<hw>For"mu*la*ry</hw>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Formularies</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>formulaire</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A book containing stated
and prescribed forms, as of oaths, declarations, prayers, medical
formula⟦ae⟧, etc.; a book of precedents.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Prescribed form or model; formula.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Formulate</ent>⟦br⟧
